&lt;LI&gt;Pilot check operates with 50% of operating pressure&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;One-touch connection for supply air only&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Available in 6-10mm and 1/4&quot;-1/2&quot; tube sizes&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Universal style connection standard&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Thread sealant is standard&lt;/LI&gt;
&lt;LI&gt;Available in PT, NPT, and G thread (standard)&lt;/LI&gt;&lt;/UL&gt;

